main.java.controllers

Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.controllers.Controller
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    The most important object in the program. Controller implements the Runnable interface, runs in a thread, contains references to every object in the application (directly or indirectly) and organises everything.
    Author:
    Naichiri
